'''Moradabad-e Posht Rig''' ({{langx|fa|مراد اباد پشت ريگ}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''Morādābād-e Posht Rīg''') is a village in [[Chahdegal Rural District]], [[Negin Kavir District]], [[Fahraj County]], [[Kerman Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 88, in 17 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|08}}</ref>
