{{short description|Bermudian cricketer}} {{Use dmy dates|date=April 2022}} {{Infobox cricketer | name = B. A. Brathwaite | image = | country = Bermuda | fullname = B. A. Brathwaite | birth_date = | birth_place = | batting = | bowling = | role = | international = | club1 = [[Bermuda cricket team|Bermuda]] | year1 = 1996/97–1998/99 | clubnumber1 = | columns = 1 | column1 = [[List A cricket|List A]] | matches1 = 6 | runs1 = 12 | bat avg1 = 6.00 | 100s/50s1 = 0/0 | top score1 = 10 | deliveries1 = 144 | wickets1 = 3 | bowl avg1 = 51.66 | fivefor1 = 0 | tenfor1 = 0 | best bowling1 = 1/16 | catches/stumpings1 = 1/– | date = 19 March | year = 2012 | source = http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/23711.html Cricinfo }}
'''B. A. Brathwaite''' (born 1 January 1970) is a former [[Bermuda|Bermudian]] [[cricket]]er. Brathwaite's [[batting (cricket)|batting]] and [[bowling (cricket)|bowling]] styles are unknown.
Brathwaite made his debut for [[Bermuda cricket team|Bermuda]] in a [[List A cricket|List A]] match against the [[Windward Islands cricket team|Windward Islands]] in the 1996–97 Shell/Sandals Trophy, with him making three further List A appearances in that seasons tournament.<ref name="LAM">{{cite web |url-access=subscription |url=https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/21/21096/List_A_Matches.html|title=List A Matches played by BA Brathwaite|publisher=CricketArchive|accessdate=19 March 2013}}</ref> He later further made two List A appearances in the [[1998–99 Red Stripe Bowl]] against [[Trinidad and Tobago national cricket team|Trinidad and Tobago]] and the Windward Islands.<ref name="LAM"/> He scored a total of 12 runs in his six matches,<ref>{{cite web |url-access=subscription |url=https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/21/21096/a_Batting_by_Team.html|title=List A Batting and Fielding For Each Team by BA Brathwaite|publisher=CricketArchive|accessdate=19 March 2013}}</ref> as well as taking three wickets from a total of 24 [[over (cricket)|overs]] bowled.<ref>{{cite web |url-access=subscription |url=https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/21/21096/a_Bowling_by_Team.html|title=List A Bowling For Each Team by BA Brathwaite|publisher=CricketArchive|accessdate=19 March 2013}}</ref>
